---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../../css/services.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Systems & Software Design | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional systems architecture and software design services in the UAE. We design scalable, resilient, and secure systems for businesses of all sizes."
  path="/services/systems-design/"
  image="/img/og-systems.jpg"
>
  <section class="service-content" id="systems-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2 class="service-title">Systems & Software Design</h2>
      <p>
        Great software starts with great design. At GeneralSoft, we provide professional systems architecture 
        and software design services that lay the foundation for scalable, maintainable, and high-performance 
        applications. Our team of experienced architects works with you to design systems that meet your 
        current needs while anticipating future growth.
      </p>
      <p>
        From microservices architecture to event-driven systems, from API design to database schema planning, 
        we bring decades of combined experience to every project. We document our designs thoroughly, ensuring 
        your team has a clear blueprint to follow during implementation.
      </p>

      <h3>Our Design Services</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>System Architecture</h4>
          <p>Design of scalable, resilient system architectures including microservices, serverless, and hybrid cloud deployments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>API Design</h4>
          <p>RESTful and GraphQL API design with comprehensive documentation, versioning strategies, and security best practices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Database Design</h4>
          <p>Schema design, data modeling, and optimization for relational and NoSQL databases to ensure performance at scale.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Technical Documentation</h4>
          <p>Comprehensive architecture documentation, design decision records, and runbooks for your development and operations teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Our Design Process</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Requirements Analysis:</strong> Understanding functional and non-functional requirements</li>
        <li><strong>Technology Selection:</strong> Choosing the right tools and platforms for your use case</li>
        <li><strong>Architecture Design:</strong> Creating detailed system architecture diagrams and specifications</li>
        <li><strong>Design Review:</strong> Peer review and validation against requirements and best practices</li>
        <li><strong>Implementation Support:</strong> Guiding your development team through the implementation phase</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Projects Proof Section -->
      <div class="projects-proof">
        <h3>Proven Architecture Delivery — Projects Completed</h3>
        <p>
          Our architecture portfolio spans enterprise-scale integration
          platforms, healthcare exchanges, and cloud migration programs.
        </p>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Enterprise Service Bus — Financial Services</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Oct 2006 – Feb 2007</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Implemented an Enterprise Service Bus (ESB) architecture involving
            Microsoft Dynamics, SQL Server 2005 (Integration Services,
            Reporting Services, OLAP/ADOMD.Net), BizTalk 2006 (Pipelines, EDI,
            Orchestration, Rule Engine), and SharePoint 2003/2007. The ESB
            connected multiple line-of-business systems with a unified
            messaging and orchestration layer.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">ESB</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk 2006</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SQL Server</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SharePoint</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Dynamics</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">EDI</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Healthcare Exchange — Obama Care Initiative</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jan 2013 – Dec 2013</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Designed a Healthcare Exchange based on the Affordable Care Act
            ("Obama Care") initiative. Extended Dynamics CRM SDK with custom
            IFRAME forms using Xrm.Page/Xrm.Utility and Ribbon customization
            (RibbonDiffXml). Refactored and ported HIPAA 5010 implementations
            to BizTalk 2013. Created EDI Viewers for HTML5 and Windows Phone,
            and deployed document routing on Azure for EDI X12 transactions
            (837, 835, 834, 270). Implemented business rules based on
            geo-spatial criteria.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk 2013</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Dynamics CRM</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">HIPAA</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">EDI X12</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Trizetto Facets</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Enterprise Integration — Global Law Firm</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Dec 2013 – Aug 2014</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Managed TFS installation and configuration for a global law firm.
            Developed customizations for Elite 3E and IntApp integration.
            Improved configuration management and validated production
            artefacts. Refactored BizTalk solution for zero-touch deployment
            using ESB Toolkit 2.1/2.2. The integration connected multiple
            practice management, billing, and HR systems.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk 2010/2013</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">ESB Toolkit</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Elite 3E</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">PeopleSoft</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">TFS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SSIS</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>ERP Migration — BizTalk 2009 to 2013 R2</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Oct 2014 – Jan 2015</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Refactored legacy BizTalk 2009 implementation to BizTalk 2013 R2
            with ESB Toolkit 2.3 and Azure SDK 2.3. Built corporate store apps
            for Windows Phone and Windows RT. Set up Lab Management on Azure
            for automated test suites. Integrated Azure AD with on-premises AD
            and Exchange. The migration covered SAP, Oracle, Dynamics CRM, and
            SharePoint integration.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk 2013 R2</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SAP</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Oracle</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Dynamics CRM</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">ESB 2.3</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">

    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Common questions about our systems design services.</p>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details>
            <summary>Do you design systems for startups or only enterprises?</summary>
            <p>We work with businesses of all sizes. For startups, we design lean architectures that can scale cost-effectively. For enterprises, we focus on robustness, security, and integration with existing systems.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Can you review and improve our existing system design?</summary>
            <p>Yes. We offer architecture review services where we analyze your current system design, identify bottlenecks and risks, and provide recommendations for improvement.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-content">
        <h2>Design Your System Right the First Time</h2>
        <p>Contact our architecture team to discuss your project and get expert guidance on system design.</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <a href="/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br />Get in touch</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
